I've been secretly training, wanting to catch up
to Amelia quickly.

enrolling in the academy?
Well, that's the kind of feeling.
Hehe, that makes big sister happy too.

from now on.

(I'm glad she didn't suspect anything, but I need
to confirm with Leviathan)

know.

And besides, the lock is still on with magic. It's
really troublesome.
